dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from an email from UNOCHA. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field. 2. Date value changed from "12/6/2020" to "6/12/2020" to match value in Admin1. 3. Fixed 2 multipart sliver errors. 4. Admin0 p-code changed from 3 letter ISO code to 2 letter ISO code. 5. Admin1 "Trarza" p-code changed to "MR12" to match Admin1 layer. 6. Admin1 "Tris-Zemmour" p-code changed to "MR13" to match Admin1 layer. 7. Admin1 "Tris Zemmour" spelling changed to "Tris-Zemmour" to match Admin1 layer. 8. Admin1 "Hodh El Chargui" spelling changed to "Hodh El Chargi" to match Admin1 layer. 9. Fixed nesting error between Admin2 "Eayoune El Atrous" and Admin1 "Hodh El Gharbi".
